name: SINGLE Shabby Flower Headband/clip   30+ colors
description:
Every outfit needs to be accessorized. Yes..even for babies! These shabby flower headbands/clips are a great way to add color, texture and pop to any outfit. We have 30+ colors and designs to pick from. Great for ALL ages. Newborn - Adult

Each flower comes with a standard Jewel, Pearl or accent bow and with a color coordinating elastic or clip. 

Please complete your order and then "Send a note" to us with your preference of Elastic or clip, and what size. If you have a special request or custom design(like a specific center piece), please use this same note to let us know what you want. We LOVE custom orders, and would love to work with you on creating something beautiful that YOU love! **"Send a note" is located at the top of the website**


*may contain small pieces. Please use with adult supervision only.**

name: Stretch Wraps
description:
These beautiful Stretch wraps are perfect for wrapping baby in. With tons of stretch to them, they make swaddling extra easy. 

Size is 16in. x 64in. unstretched. Size can be easily doubled when pulled to swaddle. 

Perfect for a Newborn session, as a Maternity belly wrap, or even for a new mama as a light weight swaddle wrap. 

Always use with adult supervision only. 

If wrap color is "in stock", they will ship out between 1-3 days. If wrap color is out of stock, they will ship out in 10-14 days. Please contact me before you place your wrap order if you would like to know what colors are in stock at the time.
